-- BlackRock’s Fink Says ECB Plan to Bring Stability to Europe
-- B y   A l e x i s   L e o n d i s
-- 2012-09-10T12:36:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-10/blackrock-s-fink-says-ecb-plan-to-bring-stability-to-europe.html
BlackRock Inc. (BLK) ’s Chief Executive
Officer Laurence D. Fink said the European Central Bank’s plan
to buy government debt will stabilize the European bond markets.  “I do believe the tail risks have been reduced by what the
ECB has announced,” Fink said today at the Barclays 2012
Financial Services Conference in New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
